# Raw Solana secret keys — one per line — used by the Solana modes.
# Two formats are auto-detected:
#   1. base58 string (Phantom "Export Private Key" — ~88 chars, no brackets)
#   2. JSON byte array (Solana CLI keypair files — `[12,34,56,...]`, 64 bytes)
# Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# The wizard creates this file automatically when you paste secrets in the
# Solana-side prompt; you normally don't need to edit it by hand.
